self.setUpClass()
num_qubits = 1
p = ql.Program('test_usingqx_sparse2qubitotherqubit_test', platform, num_qubits
    )
k = ql.Kernel('akernel', platform, num_qubits)
matrix = [0.30279949 - 0.60010283j, -0.58058628 - 0.45946559j, 0.04481146 -
    0.73904059j, 0.64910478 + 0.17456782j]
u1 = ql.Unitary('testname', matrix)
u1.decompose()
k.gate(u1, [0])
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
qx.set(os.path.join(output_dir, p.name + '_initialqasmwriter_out.qasm'))
qx.execute()
c0 = qx.get_state()
self.assertAlmostEqual(helper_prob(matrix[0]), helper_regex(c0)[0], 5)
self.assertAlmostEqual(helper_prob(matrix[1]), helper_regex(c0)[1], 5)
